Follow the instructions below and apply for a yelp developer account(https://www.yelp.com/fusion) to attain API Key.
How to operate:
First enter a state you would like to search. 
After searching, the system will generate top ten cities in the state you entered.
Then enter a number corresponded to the city and the system will tell you if its fetching data or inserting data.
Then the system will ask user if they would like to see the chart.
-Yes (display chart in a different window)
  - then ask you to enter a another city (Choose a number for detail search or "exit" or "back")
-No 
  - then ask you to start over (Enter a state name (e.g. Michigan, michigan) that you want to visit or "exit")
